<div class="comment-content">
<p>This is still chinese, right?<br/>
With all that &#8220;baka&#8221; here &#8220;baka&#8221; there, I can hardly believe that&#8230; this is probably the most infuriating translation on wuxiaworld.</p>
</div> 
